    <release version="II v1.2" date="2008-11-16" description="new version of ppwcode exception util">
      <action dev="jandockx@gmail.com" type="update">
        We now only use the split of part in ppwcode exception util, and no longer the exception
        vernacular. This is only an implementation issue.
      </action>
    </release>
    <release version="II v1.1" date="2008-10-01" description="new version of ppwcode exception vernacular">
      <action dev="jandockx@gmail.com" type="update">
        Via a new parent pom, we use the first non-snapshot release of the ppwcode
        exception vernacular. Here, there is one class name changed, and we changed this code
        accordingly. This is only an implementation issue.
      </action>
    </release>
    <release version="II v1.0" date="2008-09-30" description="big cleanup">
      <action dev="jandockx@gmail.com" type="update">
        Moved project from PeopleWare to ppwcode. Packages thus have new names.
        This is the natural child of ppw-i18n-I
      </action>
      <action dev="jandockx@gmail.com" type="update">
        Using Toryt annotations for contracts.
      </action>
      <action dev="jandockx@gmail.com" type="update">
        ResourceBundleLoadStrategy now throws exceptions when the resource bundle is
        not found, instead of returning null.
      </action>
    </release>

